import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import React from 'react'
import App from './App'

import axios from 'axios'

axios
.get('http://localhost:3001/notes')
.then(response => {
  const notes = response.data
  console.log('', notes)

  ReactDOM.render(<App notes={notes} />,document.getElementById('root'))
})
